{"tid":490931,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屌 究竟我係咪拍緊拖","createTime":"2017-12-06T05:04:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T20:55:04.000Z","uid":26852,"like":247,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"85843598d6b5cac33f7f8bca3d9813e64ec55afa","tid":490931,"uid":26852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T05:04:34.000Z","msg":"由一開始拍拖到而家幾年時間 <br />\n佢一直都係處於極度不信任我嘅狀態<br />\n我真係唔知佢係睇得人地太多帽事定係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無論我點樣斷絕同異性嘅任何接觸 點樣世界得返佢一個 冇朋友 連on個 whatsapp都只可以覆佢 on多一秒都會換黎不停追問點解on多左一秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n另外對佢黎講cap圖報告每個鐘行程是常識吧 但佢亦覺得就算有圖都唔代表張圖係真嘅 <br />\n<br />\n你地可能會覺得佢好得閒 錯啦 佢唔得閒架 成日都好忙 只係一得閒嘅時候 只會係拎我嘅行程報告 同埋要審下佢個犯 姐係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其他正常情侶交流同關心 係完全零<br />\n佢每日只需要確保我係佢口中嘅好乖 佢就唔會理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頭先又發生件事 有個唔撚識嘅異性搵我 我就好似平時咁報告 cap圖佢睇 <br />\n點知佢就開始黎料 佢首先立即打比對方屌鳩人 之後再係咁屌鳩我同人會一直聯絡 再話我唔會block鳩對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實有冇人話我知 我究竟係咪拍緊拖？我好撚攰好撚心淡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每日無限loop真係人都癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c62ef95f22d2a07a63eba4a131cc9c80e450de","tid":490931,"uid":23170,"like":149,"dislike":1,"score":148,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T05:05:54.000Z","msg":"飛左佢la"},{"pid":"3eb3e1168bb302956cdebff316d863f9bcaf71c5","tid":490931,"uid":157579,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T05:06:10.000Z","msg":"笑"},{"pid":"c66c1f99be35ac8129120781c495767ce1c17d44","tid":490931,"uid":83531,"like":24,